nodes.text: An extraction of deserted clone CC-5576 was conducted by the rogue Clone Force 99 on Daro, at a secret Imperial installation. Clone Force 99 managed to successfully rescue CC-5576, named Gregor, but encountered large forces of commandos and TK troopers. Additional V-wing starfighters and craft prevented a successful escape, resulting in the capture of Clone Force 99 leader "Hunter."
